mappings.name: Returns the requested MAC address pool. - 404
Returns the requested MAC address pool. (application/json)

schema.description: This resource represents a MAC address pool.  The default MAC address pools are used if you set the MAC address type for a virtual machine to 'Static'.  If the virtual machine setting is 'Dynamic', the hypervisor assigns the MAC address.

location.description: The region where the resource is located.

Returns a list of all MAC address pools at a location. (application/json)

schema.description: A pageable list of MAC address pools.
